---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Meet the creator of Smartivate Hub." />
		<style>
			.about-hero { padding: 5rem 1rem; text-align: center; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 20px; margin: 2rem auto; max-width: 1200px; }
			.about-hero h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
			
			.content-section { max-width: 800px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #334155; font-size: 1.1rem; }
			.content-section h2 { color: #0f172a; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
			
			.ecosystem-box { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
			.eco-card { padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; background: white; }
			.eco-card h3 { color: #4f46e5; margin-top: 0; }
			
			.mission-statement { background: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; margin-top: 4rem; }
			
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.about-hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
				.ecosystem-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="about-hero">
				<span style="color: #4f46e5; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">The Story Behind</span>
				<h1>Smartivate Hub</h1>
				<p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #64748b; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
					Helping you learn, build, and grow using modern technology and AI.
				</p>
			</section>

			<article class="content-section">
				<p>Welcome to <strong>Smartivate Hub</strong> — a platform focused on helping you learn, build, and grow using modern technology and AI.</p>
				<p>My name is <strong>Kojo Nketia Mensah</strong>, and I created Smartivate Hub to make tech easier to understand and more practical to apply.</p>

				<h2>My Journey</h2>
				<p>I started like many beginners — overwhelmed by complex tutorials and unclear instructions. Instead of just watching content, I decided to start building real projects and experimenting with tools like AI, web development frameworks, and automation systems.</p>
				<p>Over time, I realized that most people don’t need more tools — they need better guidance.</p>

				<div class="ecosystem-box">
					<div class="eco-card">
						<h3>Smartivate Hub</h3>
						<p>Your learning center. Here you explore concepts through guides, tutorials, and projects.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="eco-card">
						<h3>Smartivate Pro</h3>
						<p>Your execution center. Access powerful AI and automation tools at <a href="http://www.smartivatepro.com" style="color: #4f46e5;">smartivatepro.com</a>.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<h2>What You’ll Learn</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Clear and simple guides on complex tech</li>
					<li>Step-by-step tutorials for modern tools</li>
					<li>Real-world projects built from scratch</li>
					<li>Practical workflows you can apply immediately</li>
				</ul>

				<div class="mission-statement">
					<h2>Our Mission</h2>
					<p style="font-size: 1.2rem;">To help you go from beginner to confident builder by focusing on practical skills that actually work.</p>
				</div>
			</article>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>